data.description: Beautiful custom built brick home on three quarters of an acre in cul-de sac. Home was set up with a mother in law suite sharing two bedrooms and a walk in shower. Luxurious kitchen with double wall ovens, propane stove and dishwasher. Enjoy breakfast by the fireplace in the breakfast area/ keeping area or at the extended bar that doubles is fantastic counter space for holiday cooking. Don't forget the large screened back porch. Split floor plan and a wonderful teen suite upstairs. A double car garage and a single car garage
